<bibRefCitation author="Bauer" box="[742,886,1158,1182]" pageId="32" pageNumber="483" refString="Bauer, A. M. (2014 e) Afroedura langi (FitzSimons, 1930). In: Bates, M. F., Branch, W. R., Bauer, A. M., Burger, M., Marais, J., Alexander, G. J. &amp; de Villiers, M. (Eds.), Atlas and Red List of the Reptiles of South Africa, Lesotho and Swaziland. Suricata, 1. South African National Biodiversity Institute, Pretoria, pp. 93 - 94." type="journal article" year="2014" yearSuffix="e">
